</figureCitation>
, 
<figureCitation id="AAB02A4CC221A347FEE70115FEAFFCBA" box="[350,381,810,836]" captionStart="FIGURES 41 – 48" captionStartId="13.[151,269,1756,1780]" captionTargetBox="[309,1282,514,1715]" captionTargetId="figure@13.[303,1283,514,1254]" captionTargetPageId="13" captionText="FIGURES 41 – 48. Morphological aspects of female genitalia (macerated) of Chromagallia species. (41) C. lamasi sp. nov., sternites V, VI, and VII, ventral view. (42) C. lanceolata sp. nov., sternite VII, ventral view. (43, 44) C. paraguayensis sp. nov., sternite VII, (43) ventral view, (44) caudal view. Second valvula of ovipositor, general lateral view: (45) C. lamasi sp. nov.; (46) C. zanolae sp. nov.; (47) C. lanceolata sp. nov.; (48) C. paraguayensis sp. nov. DHA: dorsal hyaline area; DP: dorsal prominence." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/181701/files/figure.png" pageId="1" pageNumber="2">45</figureCitation>
